lead_paragraph: England's Ben Stokes and Jonny Bairstow struck half centuries to guide the hosts to a four-wicket victory over Pakistan in the fourth one-day international in Leeds on Thursday as they went 4-0 ahead in the five-match series.

headline.print_headline: Stokes, Bairstow Guide England to 4-0 ODI Lead Over Pakistan
